<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
<head>
    <!-- $title = News Single page -->
    <!-- @include assets/meta-head.kit -->
</head>
<body>


<!-- @include assets/header.kit -->


<div id="main-page-wrap">

    <!-- ========= Main Content Section ========= -->
    <article class="after-header container big-padding news-single">

        <!-- Metadata & Title(article header) -->
        <header>
            <time datetime="2014-12-05" pubdate>December 5, 2014</time>
            <h1 class="title">Sell a Product, Don’t Settle for Change</h1>
        </header>

        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="img-container"><img src="images/news/big1.jpg" alt=""/></div>

        <!-- Article text -->
        <p>Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam</p>

        <!-- Text in two columns -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6"><p class="nolast">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</p></div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6"><p class="nolast">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</p></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tags & Sharing -->
        <footer class="row">
            <div class="tags-list col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                <a href="#">Travel</a> <a href="#">Lifestyle</a> <a href="#">Food</a>
            </div>

            <div class="share-col col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                <span class="headings-color">Share on:</span>
                <div class="social-likes social-likes_rounded" data-single-title="Share">
                    <div class="facebook" title="Share link on Facebook">Facebook</div>
                    <div class="twitter" title="Share link on Twitter">Twitter</div>
                    <div class="plusone" title="Share link on Google+">Google+</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>

    </article>


    <!-- ========= Navigation & Author info ========= -->
    <section class="container-wrap secondary-bg">

        <!-- Navigation links -->
        <!-- to reveal this block - just remove "hide" class -->
        <nav class="row links-row hide">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                <a href="#" class="prev-link"><i class="entypo left-open-mini"></i> Previous post</a>
            </div>

            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                <a href="#" class="next-link">Next post <i class="entypo right-open-mini"></i></a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <!-- Author info -->
        <section class="container md-padding authorinfo"><div class="row">

            <!-- avatar -->
            <div class="avatar-col hidden-xs col-xs-12 col-sm-3 col-md-2" data-mh="news-authorinfo">
                <img src="images/avatar/6.jpg" alt=""/>
            </div>

            <!-- text -->
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-9 col-md-10" data-mh="news-authorinfo">
                <h1 class="name">WPHunters</h1>

                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, cotur acing elit. Ut euis eget dolor sit amet congue. Ut vira codo matis. Sed lacia luctus magna ut sodales.</p>

                <ul class="socials-list invert">
                    <li><a href="#"><i class="entypo facebook"></i></a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><i class="entypo twitter"></i></a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><i class="entypo gplus"></i></a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div></section>

    </section>


    <!-- ========= Comments section ========= -->
    <section class="container md-padding comments-block">
        <h1 class="title">3 comments</h1>

        <!-- Comments flow -->
        <div class="flow">
            <article class="row depth-1">
                <!-- author photo -->
                <div class="avatar-col hidden-xs col-sm-1"><img src="images/nophoto.jpg" alt=""/></div>

                <!-- comment text & info -->
                <div class="comment-col col-sm-11">
                    <div class="name">Amanda</div>
                    <time datetime="2013-05-29 19:45" pubdate>May 29, 2013 at 7:45 AM</time>

                    <div class="text">Quis autem vel eum iure reprehenderit qui in ea voluptate velit esse quam nihil molestiae Quis autem vel eum iure reprehenderit qui in ea voluptate velit esse quam nihil molestiae</div>

                    <footer><a class="text-uppercase" href="#">Reply</a></footer>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- nested comment (depth=2) -->
            <article class="row depth-2">
                <!-- author photo -->
                <div class="avatar-col hidden-xs col-sm-1"><img src="images/avatar/4.jpg" alt=""/></div>

                <!-- comment text & info -->
                <div class="comment-col col-sm-11">
                    <div class="name">James</div>
                    <time datetime="2013-05-30 14:02" pubdate>May 30, 2013 at 2:02 PM</time>

                    <div class="text">Deleniti potenti venenatis eos! Hendrerit velit quisquam natoque faucibus vivamus, habitasse quo est possimus dictumst imperdiet, felis, diam consequuntur magnam.</div>

                    <footer><a class="text-uppercase" href="#">Reply</a></footer>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="row depth-2">
                <!-- author photo -->
                <div class="avatar-col hidden-xs col-sm-1"><img src="images/avatar/5.jpg" alt=""/></div>

                <!-- comment text & info -->
                <div class="comment-col col-sm-11">
                    <div class="name">Michael</div>
                    <time datetime="2013-06-01 23:33" pubdate>June 1, 2013 at 11:33 PM</time>

                    <div class="text">Proident vulputate nullam posuere, facilisi, scelerisque aute duis accusamus eros euismod doloremque hendrerit quod repellendus, a perspiciatis, magnam phasellus fusce.</div>

                    <footer><a class="text-uppercase" href="#">Reply</a></footer>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="row depth-1">
                <!-- author photo -->
                <div class="avatar-col hidden-xs col-sm-1"><img src="images/avatar/2.jpg" alt=""/></div>

                <!-- comment text & info -->
                <div class="comment-col col-sm-11">
                    <div class="name">Megan</div>
                    <time datetime="2013-06-02 22:15" pubdate>June 2, 2013 at 10:15 AM</time>

                    <div class="text">Doloribus facilisi quidem nam illum nascetur conubia deleniti nostrum luctus eum fringilla ante laboris pede mollitia, cras, harum fermentum porta.</div>

                    <footer><a class="text-uppercase" href="#">Reply</a></footer>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>


        <!-- Add comment form -->
        <h1 class="title add-comment">Add comment</h1>

        <form id="addcomment_form" action="#" method="post">

            <!-- Success message -->
            <div class="alert alert-success hide-soft">
                <strong>Well done!</strong> Your comment successfully submitted! Thank you ;)
            </div>

            <!-- Error message -->
            <div class="alert alert-danger hide-soft">
                <strong>Something wrong!</strong> <span></span>
            </div>

            <!-- Form First row -->
            <div class="row">
                <div class="form-group col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                    <label for="fullname_field">Full Name*</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="fullname_field" name="fullname" required/>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                    <label for="email_field">Email*</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email_field" name="email" required/>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Third row -->
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="message_field">Message*</label>
                <textarea id="message_field" class="form-control" rows="5" name="message" required></textarea>
            </div>

            <!-- Buttons -->
            <div class="form-group"><button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-long text-uppercase">Submit</button></div>
        </form>

    </section>

</div>


<!-- @include assets/footer.kit -->


</body>
</html>